      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello, I&amp;rsquo;m Stephane, an Unreal Engine 5 Technical Artist in the Virtual Reality industry, but I will only focus on my personal project on here. This blog is a way for me to share my progress and understanding of the Unreal Engine 4 rendering pipeline, through the development of a custom version of the engine, as well as game development.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Throughout the blog, I will refer to my custom version of Unreal as [[Ephemere Engine]], to make it easier to distinct from the vanilla version of Unreal Engine.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
